{"code_vdb_path":null,"doc_vdb_path":null,"code_index_path":".cache/am_cache/code_index/tantivy/98feb757f55b98e9","cve_intel":[{"vuln_id":"CVE-2025-24970","ghsa":{"ghsa_id":"GHSA-4g8c-wm8x-jfhw","cve_id":"CVE-2025-24970","summary":"SslHandler doesn't correctly validate packets which can lead to native crash when using native SSLEngine","description":"### Impact
When a special crafted packet is received via SslHandler it doesn't correctly handle validation of such a packet in all cases which can lead to a native crash.

### Workarounds
As workaround its possible to either disable the usage of the native SSLEngine or changing the code from:

```
SslContext context = ...;
SslHandler handler = context.newHandler(....);
```

to:

```
SslContext context = ...;
SSLEngine engine = context.newEngine(....);
SslHandler handler = new SslHandler(engine, ....);
```","severity":"high","vulnerabilities":[{"package":{"ecosystem":"maven","name":"io.netty:netty-handler"},"vulnerable_version_range":">= 4.1.91.Final, <= 4.1.117.Final","first_patched_version":"4.1.118.Final","vulnerable_functions":[]}],"cvss":{"score":7.5,"vector_string":"CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H"},"cwes":[{"cwe_id":"CWE-20","name":"Improper Input Validation"}],"published_at":"2025-02-10T17:38:10Z","updated_at":"2025-04-16T19:30:04Z","url":"https://api.github.com/advisories/GHSA-4g8c-wm8x-jfhw","html_url":"https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-4g8c-wm8x-jfhw","type":"reviewed","repository_advisory_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty/security-advisories/GHSA-4g8c-wm8x-jfhw","source_code_location":"https://github.com/netty/netty","identifiers":[{"value":"GHSA-4g8c-wm8x-jfhw","type":"GHSA"},{"value":"CVE-2025-24970","type":"CVE"}],"references":["https://github.com/netty/netty/security/advisories/GHSA-4g8c-wm8x-jfhw","https://github.com/netty/netty/commit/87f40725155b2f89adfde68c7732f97c153676c4","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-24970","https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20250221-0005","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-24970-netty-vulnerability-detection","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-24970-netty-vulnerability-mitigation","https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-4g8c-wm8x-jfhw"],"github_reviewed_at":"2025-02-10T17:38:10Z","nvd_published_at":"2025-02-10T22:15:38Z","withdrawn_at":null,"cvss_severities":{"cvss_v3":{"vector_string":"CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H","score":7.5},"cvss_v4":{"vector_string":null,"score":0.0}},"credits":[{"user":{"login":"johnou","id":323497,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMyMzQ5Nw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/323497?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/johnou","html_url":"https://github.com/johnou","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/johnou/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/johnou/follo